        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Law Firms & Professional Services</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Birmingham's legal and professional community expects excellence:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Conference room presentation standards</li>
              <li>✓ Reception area polish</li>
              <li>✓ Document security awareness</li>
              <li>✓ After-hours cleaning protocols</li>
              <li>✓ High-end finish care</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Medical & Dental Offices</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Healthcare facilities need specialized attention:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Hospital-grade disinfectants</li>
              <li>✓ Exam room sanitization</li>
              <li>✓ Waiting area cleanliness</li>
              <li>✓ HIPAA-compliant staff</li>
              <li>✓ Biohazard awareness</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Restaurants & Food Service</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Birmingham's food scene demands cleanliness:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Kitchen degreasing</li>
              <li>✓ Hood and exhaust cleaning</li>
              <li>✓ Health department compliance</li>
              <li>✓ Dining area presentation</li>
              <li>✓ Bar and brewery cleaning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Retail & Showrooms</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Customer-facing spaces need daily attention:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Floor maintenance</li>
              <li>✓ Glass and display cleaning</li>
              <li>✓ Fitting room sanitization</li>
              <li>✓ Storefront presentation</li>
              <li>✓ High-traffic area focus</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DOWNTOWN SECTION -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Downtown Birmingham High-Rise Cleaning</h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Downtown office buildings have specific considerations:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">High-Rise Protocols</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li><strong>Building coordination:</strong> We work with property management on access, elevator scheduling, and security.</li>
            <li><strong>After-hours access:</strong> Most downtown cleaning happens evenings or early mornings. We coordinate badge access and security check-ins.</li>
            <li><strong>Freight elevators:</strong> Equipment transport follows building protocols.</li>
            <li><strong>Multi-tenant floors:</strong> We respect shared spaces and neighboring businesses.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

