          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">How much does commercial cleaning cost in Birmingham?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Commercial cleaning in Birmingham typically costs $0.10-$0.18 per square foot. A 2,000 sq ft office cleaned 2-3 times weekly runs $350-$700/month. Downtown and Mountain Brook are at the higher end; suburban areas are more moderate.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Do you clean downtown high-rise offices?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Yes, we serve businesses throughout downtown Birmingham. We coordinate with building management on access, elevator usage, and security protocols. After-hours cleaning is standard for most downtown locations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Do you clean after business hours?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Yes, most commercial cleaning happens after hours. Evening, early morning, and weekend schedules are available. We work around your business operations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Are your cleaners insured and background-checked?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Yes. All commercial cleaning staff are insured and background-checked. We understand the security and trust requirements of Birmingham businesses.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Get a Commercial Cleaning Quote</h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Every business is different. Tell us about your space, location, and needs, and we'll provide a customized quote.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Professional Clean for the Magic City</p>
